debates.showAs: Sale of Tickets (Cultural, Entertainment, Recreational and Sporting Events) (Amendment) Bill 2024: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Sale of Tickets (Cultural, Entertainment, Recreational and Sporting Events) Act 2021 so as to prohibit a primary ticket seller from engaging in dynamic pricing when selling, or advertising for sale, tickets or ticket packages for cultural, entertainment, recreational and sporting events, and to promote fairer access to tickets by prohibiting the sale, or advertising for sale, of tickets or ticket packages for a price that is adjusted or set by dynamic pricing to meet increased demand.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú an Achta um Dhíol Ticéad (Imeachtaí Cultúir, Siamsaíochta, Áineasa agus Spóirt), 2021 d’fhonn toirmeasc a chur ar phríomhdhíoltóir ticéad a bheith ag gabháil do phraghsáil dhinimiciúil tráth a bheidh ticéid nó pacáistí ticéad le haghaidh imeachtaí cultúir, siamsaíochta, áineasa agus spóirt á ndíol nó tráth a bheidh ticéid nó pacáistí ticéad le haghaidh imeachtaí den sórt sin á bhfógairt lena ndíol, agus d’fhonn rochtain ar thicéid ar bhonn níos córa a chur chun cinn trí thoirmeasc a chur le ticéid nó le pacáistí ticéad a dhíol, nó le ticéid nó le pacáistí ticéad a fhógairt lena ndíol, ar phraghas a dhéantar a choigeartú nó a shocrú le praghsáil dhinimiciúil chun freastal ar an méadú ar éileamh.
bill.shortTitleEn: Sale of Tickets (Cultural, Entertainment, Recreational and Sporting Events) (Amendment) Bill 2024
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Dhíol Ticéad (Imeachtaí Cultúir, Siamsaíochta, Áineasa agus Spóirt) (Leasú), 2024

debates.showAs: Maternity Protection (Amendment) Bill 2024: Committee and Remaining Stages
Maternity Protection (Amendment) Bill 2024: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend and extend the Maternity Protection Act 1994 and to provide for postponement of maternity leave where a mother has been diagnosed with cancer or other serious illness during pregnancy, and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú agus do leathnú an Achta um Chosaint Mháithreachais, 1994 agus do dhéanamh socrú maidir le saoire mháithreachais a iarchur i gcás gur fáthmheasadh go bhfuil ailse nó breoiteacht thromaí eile ar mháthair le linn toirchis, agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.

debates.showAs: Ukraine Solidarity Bill 2022: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide comprehensive solidarity to Ukraine in the face of the unlawful war of aggression waged by the Russian Federation with the support of Belarus, to provide for criminal and civil liability in respect of the crime of aggression and related wrongs and for the recognition of qualifications of displaced persons, to make provision with extra-territorial effect in accordance with Article 29.8 of the Constitution and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do sholáthar dlúthpháirtíocht chuimsitheach don Úcráin i bhfianaise an chogaidh ionsaithe neamhdhleathaigh atá á fhearadh ag Cónaidhm na Rúise le tacaíocht ón mBealarúis, do dhéanamh socrú maidir le dliteanas coiriúil agus dliteanas sibhialta i leith choir an ionsaithe agus éagóracha gaolmhara agus maidir le cáilíochtaí daoine easáitithe a aithint, do dhéanamh foráil le héifeacht sheachchríochach de réir Airteagal 29.8 den Bhunreacht agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Dhlúthpháirtíocht leis an Úcráin, 2022

debates.showAs: Firearms and Offensive Weapons (Amendment) Bill 2021: Second Stage [Private Members]
Firearms and Offensive Weapons (Amendment) Bill 2021: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Firearms and Offensive Weapons Act 1990 by increasing the maximum sentence that can be imposed for the possession of a knife to cause injury to, incapacitate or intimidate any person.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú Acht na nArm Tine agus na nArm Ionsaitheach, 1990 trí mhéadú a dhéanamh ar an bpianbhreith uasta is féidir a fhorchur i leith scian a shealbhú chun díobháil a dhéanamh d’aon duine nó chun aon duine a éagumasú nó a imeaglú.
bill.shortTitleGa: Bille na nArm Tine agus na nArm Ionsaitheach (Leasú), 2021

debates.showAs: Children (Amendment) Bill 2021: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Children Act 2001 to permit the publication or broadcast of details pertaining to a person who has been charged with an offence against a child where that child is deceased, and to permit adults who were victims of an offence committed against them when they were a child to waive the anonymity provided for under the Children Act 2001.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú Acht na Leanaí, 2001 chun go gceadófar foilsiú nó craoladh mionsonraí a bhaineann le duine a cúisíodh i gcion in aghaidh linbh i gcás an leanbh sin a bheith éagtha, agus chun go gceadófar d’aosaigh ab íospartaigh chiona a rinneadh ina n-aghaidhnuair ba leanaí iad an anaithnideacht dá bhforáiltear faoi Acht na Leanaí, 2001 a tharscaoileadh.

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to protect the Central Fund of the National Lottery established under section 8 of the National Lottery Act 1986 and section 44 of the National Lottery Act 2013 by amending the Betting Acts 1931 to 2015 by introducing a condition on certain licences granted under the Betting Acts 1931 to 2015.

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Garda Síochána Acts 2005 to 2015 to provide for enhanced powers to be granted to the Policing Authority for the purpose of overseeing the performance of the Garda Commissioner and the Garda Síochána of its functions relating to policing services; to amend the provisions of the Acts relating to the Garda Síochána Inspectorate; and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú Achtanna an Gharda Síochána, 2005 go 2015 chun socrú a dhéanamh go ndeonófar cumhachtaí feabhsaithe don Údarás Póilíneachta chun maoirseacht a dhéanamh ar fheidhmíocht Choimisinéir an Gharda agus ar chomhlíonadh a fheidhmeanna maidir le seirbhísí póilíneachta ag an nGarda Síochána; do leasú fhorálacha na nAchtanna a bhaineann le Cigireacht an Gharda Síochána; agus do dhéanamh socrú maidir le nithe gaolmhara.

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Civil Liability Act 1961 to provide for the effects in civil law of the principle that a person should be precluded from benefitting from committing any homicide and the principle that no cause of action arises from one's own wrongful act, to amend the Succession Act 1965 and to provide for related matters

bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Dhliteanas Sibhialta (Leasú) (Cosc le Tairbhe a Fháil as Dúnbhású), 2017 2017
